; Coverage for xact.cc lines 633-653 (rounding adjustment in balance check)
; When a per-unit cost is used and the total is rounded differently than
; the exact accumulated cost, the rounding tolerance check allows it.

2024/01/01 Buy Bread
    Expenses:Food    3 bread @ $3.99
    Assets:Cash     $-11.97

test reg
24-Jan-01 Buy Bread             Expenses:Food               3 bread      3 bread
                                Assets:Cash                 $-11.97      $-11.97
                                                                         3 bread
end test
